txt.en: Collect Silver Tokens of Dol Amroth ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Bring the Silver Tokens to Harniel

'There are many places within the Paths of the Dead that have not seen a living soul. With the army now having departed, there is a great deal to learn from that place.\n\n'The more donations of Silver Tokens of Dol Amroth you bring me, the more progress we can make on opening the unexplored areas within the Paths of the Dead. Once that is done, there will be much to explore.'
'This will help aid us towards accomplishing the goal. Soon we should be able to open those tunnels.'

Once enough contributions have been received, the lost caves of the Paths of the Dead will be opened. With that, aspiring town guards of Dol Amroth will be able to curry favour with the Swan-knights Barracks.
Unlocking the Paths of the Dead
Harniel has asked you to bring her Silver Tokens of Dol Amroth to help pay the labour for unlocking new areas of the Paths of the Dead.
